data.description: 20 Acre Ranch sitting at the end of a private road!! Home features 4 bedrooms 2 bathrooms with a seperate living room and family room! Property has multiple outbuildings, detached 2 car garage and a seasonal creek. This property is the perfect property for those that want privacy, open views and room to roam. Bring all your animals and toys!!!
